      "dbImpact": "**INSERT** another row into `folio_lines` (same columns as AC-S7-01). **UPDATE** `folios.outstanding_balance` by the correction `amount` (here −5). The row referenced by `original_folio_line_id` in the request is **not updated** — only read for validation and description text."
